			<div class="post-8537 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-bitcoin-2 category-gata tag-cryptography tag-fifth-amendment tag-first-amendment tag-inside-bitcoins tag-jfk tag-legal-tender post_box top" id="post-8537">
